title: Captain Blood - The Classic Film Scores for Errol Flynn
description:
The greatest action hero of the 1930s into the 1950s, Errol Flynn's films were always a rollicking ride, thanks in part to the music matching the action. 

Charles Gerhardt and the National Philharmonic Orchestra recreate the best parts of those film in pristine stereo sound. Those scores include the music to The Adventures of Don Juan; The Sea Hawk; They Died with Their Boots On; Dodge City; Objective, Burma!; The Sun Also Rises and The Adventures of Robin Hood
